{"tid":1970481,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"原來安安試過咬海洋公園staff","createTime":"2020-04-13T07:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T10:07:40.000Z","uid":64131,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5703fc0dd76d1d04a8b2100a390c9d99614ef422","tid":1970481,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:38:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GY4bWo-0FSA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGY4bWo-0FSA&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWf3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=d8600789\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GY4bWo-0FSA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「國寶」大熊貓咬人！現年22歲在港居住超過9年、是香港現有四隻大熊貓中的老二「安安」，日前在海洋公園熊貓館內一名女護理員面前突然「發老脾」，在她的左腳小腿上咬了一口，女事主小腿當場披血受傷；安安傷人亦「知衰」慌忙逃回洞穴，傷者事後被送院治理，至今已留醫九天，事件懷疑有人餵飼程序出錯。消息稱，海洋公園已將意外歸類為非熊貓之錯，屬人為行政錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咬完人走佬，個pat pat 圓碌碌笑死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb0d1ad283fa7dbc74ae4d12687eecd2453dca0","tid":1970481,"uid":221055,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"如果係其他動物就會人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088814471d90fe97331b08c30228b039374ce1bd","tid":1970481,"uid":194326,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:42:37.000Z","msg":"早幾日同事同我講熊貓終於拆野生埋仔<br />\n我心諗<br />\n關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ef6fa18af8e80941bcedf7670289440b7de03d","tid":1970481,"uid":7078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:43:17.000Z","msg":"支那style"},{"pid":"83794a324d540da75ebe3e283dcea6664f9808f0","tid":1970481,"uid":9412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:43:50.000Z","msg":"走得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6220b18c9767572780884ecdd95c980c4df2e679","tid":1970481,"uid":46587,"like":2